## 3. Chat

The accounting assistant answers natural-language questions and can create/update invoices, manage clients and products, and categorise bank transactions. It is backed by an OpenAI-powered agent with 8 tools.

---

### 3.1 Send a Message

**POST** `/mobile/tenants/{tenant}/chat`
**Auth:** Required
**Permission:** `chat.view`
**Response type:** `text/event-stream` (Server-Sent Events)

Sends a message to the accounting assistant and streams the response back as SSE. The connection stays open while the AI processes the request (typically 3–10 seconds), then sends the result and closes.

**How to read the stream:**
- Listen for lines starting with `data: `
- Parse each as JSON
- The final event is the literal string `data: [DONE]` — close the connection at this point

**Request body:**

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `message` | string | Yes | The user's message (max 2000 chars) |
| `history` | array | No | Prior conversation turns for context (see format below) |

```json
{
  "message": "Create an invoice for Acme Corp for ₹5000 for consulting",
  "history": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Who are my clients?" },
    { "role": "assistant", "content": "You have 3 clients: Acme Corp, Beta Ltd, Gamma Inc." }
  ]
}
```

**History item format:**

| Field | Values |
|---|---|
| `role` | `"user"` or `"assistant"` |
| `content` | Message text |

**SSE Events — success:**

```
data: {"type":"reply","reply":"I've created invoice INV-0042 for Acme Corp...","clients":[],"products":[],"invoices":null,"invoice":{"id":42,"invoice_number":"INV-0042",...},"created_client":null,"created_product":null,"success":true}

data: [DONE]
```

**SSE Events — error:**

```
data: {"type":"error","reply":"Sorry, I encountered an error: ...","success":false}

data: [DONE]
```

**Response payload fields:**

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `type` | string | `"reply"` on success, `"error"` on failure |
| `reply` | string | The assistant's text response (markdown) |
| `clients` | array | Clients returned/created by the agent, if any |
| `products` | array | Products returned/created by the agent, if any |
| `invoices` | array\|null | Invoice list if the agent listed invoices |
| `invoice` | object\|null | Single invoice if the agent created/updated/fetched one |
| `created_client` | object\|null | Newly created client, if any |
| `created_product` | object\|null | Newly created product, if any |
| `success` | boolean | Whether the agent call succeeded |

**Postman tip:** Set the request type to `POST`, add the JSON body, and click **Send**. Postman will display the SSE data as the response body accumulates. You will see the raw event lines.

**Error responses:**

| Status | Reason |
|---|---|
| 403 | User does not have `chat.view` permission in this tenant |
| 422 | Validation failed (missing/invalid `message`) |

